    "Rules",
    "Unfair and Deceptive Practices"
  ],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Requires each food establishment to clearly and conspicuously display, when a price is shown to a customer, the total price of that food or beverage item, including any mandatory fees a customer would incur during the purchase.  Prohibits a food establishment from imposing on a customer or advertising any mandatory fees that are excessive or deceptive for any food or beverage offered by the food establishment.  Requires the Department of Commerce and Consumer Affairs to adopt rules."
    }
  ],
